node.title: One killed, four injured in horror single-car crash in Auckland's Massey
node.description: Emergency services were called to the scene in the early hours of Sunday.
node.content: ["A person is dead and another four were injured in a crash in the Auckland suburb of Massey early on Sunday.\n", "Emergency services were called to the single-car collision at the intersection of Rush Creek and Westgate Drs at about 3:40am.", "A police spokeswoman said the car had crashed into a fence.", "One person died at the scene and four others had moderate injuries.", "\"The serious crash unit attended and enquiries into the circumstances of the crash are continuing,\" the spokeswoman said.", "\"Westgate Dr near Rush Creek Dr will be closed for a short while longer while staff complete the scene examination.", "\"Diversions are in place.\""]
